name: BabyFeeder
0:
”Alexa, launch Baby Feeder”
”Alexa, ask Baby Feeder what to feed my 4 months old”
”Alexa, ask Baby Feeder what my newborn baby can eat”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: baby feeder
des:
Find out what food items you can introduce to your baby. 

Suggestions include types of Vegetables, Fruits, Meat, Dairy Products, etc. at a certain age in months. Some suggestions will repeat for a range of months. For example, same suggestion is given for babies 4 months to 5 months of age. 

DISCLAIMER: Please note that any suggestion given by this Alexa Skill is not a substitute for your baby's Doctor's advice. Always consult the Doctor when in doubt.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
